---
import ContentPageLayout from '../../layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro';
import { MapPin, Mail, Phone, User, Landmark, ShieldCheck } from 'lucide-astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<ContentPageLayout
  title="Imprint - eFlury Consulting"
  description="Imprint (Impressum) of eflury.com — provider identification per Art. 3 para. 1 lit. s of the Swiss Unfair Competition Act: business name, legal form, owner, contact, commercial-register and UID details."
  lang={lang}
  heroTitle="Imprint"
  heroSubtitle="Provider identification in accordance with Swiss law"
  lastUpdated="July 23, 2026"
  keywords="Imprint, Impressum, provider identification, UWG, sole proprietorship, contact address, eFlury Consulting"
>
  <p class="imprint-lead">Information pursuant to Art. 3 para. 1 lit. s of the Swiss Federal Act against Unfair Competition (UWG).</p>

  <div class="imprint-card">
    <div class="ic-head">
      <span class="ic-name">eFlury <span class="ic-accent">Consulting</span></span>
      <span class="ic-chip">Sole proprietorship (Switzerland)</span>
    </div>
    <dl class="ic-grid">
      <div class="ic-row">
        <dt><User size={17} /> Owner &amp; responsible for content</dt>
        <dd>Emanuel Aaron Flury</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="ic-row">
        <dt><MapPin size={17} /> Address</dt>
        <dd>Keltenweg 4<br />2540 Grenchen<br />Switzerland</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="ic-row">
        <dt><Mail size={17} /> Email</dt>
        <dd><a href="mailto:me@eflury.com">me@eflury.com</a></dd>
      </div>
      <div class="ic-row">
        <dt><Phone size={17} /> Phone</dt>
        <dd><a href="tel:+41799107787">+41 79 910 77 87</a></dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>

  <h2><Landmark size={20} class="h-icon" /> Commercial Register &amp; UID</h2>
  <div class="info-box">
    <p>eFlury Consulting is a sole proprietorship and currently <strong>not entered in the Swiss commercial register</strong>; accordingly, no UID number exists. As a sole proprietorship below the statutory revenue threshold, registration is not required (Art. 931 of the Swiss Code of Obligations) — that is fully legal, and we prefer stating it here openly rather than hiding it. As soon as an entry is made, we will publish the company number and UID right here.</p>
  </div>

  <h2><ShieldCheck size={20} class="h-icon" /> Data Protection</h2>
  <p>The controller for the processing of personal data within the meaning of the Swiss Data Protection Act (FADP) is Emanuel Aaron Flury, address as above. What data we process and how is set out in the <a href="/en/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>

  <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>We assume no liability for the correctness, accuracy, timeliness, reliability and completeness of the information on this website. Liability claims for material or immaterial damage arising from access to, use of, or non-use of the published information are excluded to the extent permitted by law. Detailed legal notices can be found in the <a href="/en/disclaimer/">Disclaimer</a>.</p>

  <h2>Liability for Links</h2>
  <p>References and links to third-party websites are outside our area of responsibility. Access to and use of such websites is at the user's own risk.</p>

  <h2>Copyright</h2>
  <p>The copyright and all other rights to content, images, photos and other files on this website belong exclusively to Emanuel Aaron Flury or the specifically named rights holders. Written consent of the copyright holder must be obtained in advance for the reproduction of any elements.</p>
</ContentPageLayout>

<style>
  .imprint-lead {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .imprint-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .ic-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
    background: var(--surface-navy);
  }

  .ic-name {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: white;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .ic-accent {
    color: var(--eflury-teal);
  }

  .ic-chip {
    padding: 0.28rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .ic-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ic-row {
    padding: 1.15rem 1.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .ic-row:nth-child(odd) {
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .ic-row dt {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.45rem;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--teal-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .ic-row dt :global(svg) {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ic-row dd {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .ic-row dd a {
    color: var(--teal-text);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .ic-row dd a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  :global(.h-icon) {
    color: var(--teal-text);
    vertical-align: -3px;
    margin-right: 0.35rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .ic-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .ic-row:nth-child(odd) {
      border-right: none;
    }

    .ic-head,
    .ic-row {
      padding-left: 1.25rem;
      padding-right: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
